FBIS4-57492 "drlat098__a94003" FBIS-LAT-94-098-A Daily Report 14 May 1994 ANNEX Brazil Prospector Claims Venezuelan Guard `Invade' Roraima Prospector Claims Venezuelan Guard `Invade' Roraima PY1605145394 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 14 May 94 p 6 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY PY1605145394 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL Portuguese BFN [From the "JB Report" column by Teodomiro Braga: "War in the North"] [Text] On 13 May, the Venezuelan National Guard again invaded Brazilian territory in Roraima, arresting gold prospectors at the Dicao airstrip. Jose Altino Machado, leader of the prospectors, criticized: "They invade our territory and arrest Brazilians, while the Brazilian Army applauds and the Foreign Ministry hides."
